हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा 
https://links.kukufm.com/gT9Adz
show.description: Travis is a rich billionaire and the CEO of a major tech company, who lost his wife to a tragic accident shortly after their wedding. As a result, he is broody and doesn't commit to relationships. Until he crosses paths with Stella one night in a bar. Stella is an escort who is short of money for her little sister's cancer treatment. She is in huge debt and is looking for a way out. Jason comes to her with an offer she can't refuse.
